00:29:39,068 --> 00:29:40,195
Un morceau de viande.

478
00:29:41,196 --> 00:29:42,572
Deux tranches de piment.

479
00:29:43,573 --> 00:29:44,741
Gousse d'ail.

480
00:29:45,700 --> 00:29:47,744
Saveurs simples mais distinctes.

481
00:29:54,459 --> 00:29:55,919
D'accord.

482
00:29:58,630 --> 00:30:00,089
Pour la viande ...

483
